Class AmbulanceLocationHandler

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.web.socket.handler.AbstractWebSocketHandler
org.springframework.web.socket.handler.TextWebSocketHandler
com.example.flexiMed.websocket.AmbulanceLocationHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.web.socket.WebSocketHandler
@Service public class AmbulanceLocationHandler extends org.springframework.web.socket.handler.TextWebSocketHandler
Handles WebSocket communication for ambulance location updates. This class extends TextWebSocketHandler to manage WebSocket sessions and send location data to specific users.
